      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_1448657743977601714.png",
                "id": "talent48103",
                "key": "Whirling Tail",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Whirling Tail"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo DMG</span> dan mengambil 1 kartu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/c810824214ed1ed7d4c4519a109c0ba5_5383113581280172853.png",
                "id": "talent41761",
                "key": "Swirling Squall ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Swirling Squall "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> dan mem<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">buang</span> semua <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bonecruncher's Energy Block</span> yang ada di Tangan. Setiap <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Buang</span> 2 kartu, akan meningkatkan DMG ini sebanyak 1 kali lipat.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/1d8d506cdab76fd7660ea285c094d231_7068271268648185149.png",
                "id": "talent68989",
                "key": "Scattershot Vortex",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Scattershot Vortex"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Menciptakan 6 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bonecruncher's Energy Block</span> saat duel dimulai dan semuanya diletakkan ke dalam Dek-mu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/1f7f5486da184cb626eb0891eeb2a204_2413678137763852162.png",
                "id": "talent49308",
                "key": "Immortal Remnants: Anemo",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Immortal Remnants: Anemo"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Kartu Peristiwa</span></p><p>Secara acak mem<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">buang</span> 1 kartu berbiaya awal Dadu Elemental tertinggi di Tanganmu dan menciptakan 1 Dadu Elemental dengan tipe elemen yang sama dengan Karakter aktifmu. (Dapat memainkan 1 kartu tersebut per Ronde)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6132454922985025852.png",
                "id": "talent45057",
                "key": "Bonecruncher's Energy Block",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/531ed6322b0a8f721e6080da7fcd72ce_2290552905979312200.png",
                "title": "Bonecruncher's Energy Block"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_3908920206934630109.png",
                "id": "talent88319",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Buang</span></strong></p><p>Gunakan efek Kartu Aksi atau Skill Karakter untuk membuang Kartu Aksi dari Tangan atau Dek-mu.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Energy</span></strong></p><p>Karakter harus mengonsumsi Energy untuk menggunakan Elemental Burst-nya.</p><p>Saat Karakter menggunakan Elemental Skill atau Normal Attack, mereka akan memperoleh 1 poin Energy.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/02/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7891715569506120501.png",
                "id": "talent76769",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
